parameters:
... I positioned the cursor on that file
and double- clicked it. When I did
that... the laptop made a clicking sound
and launched a video player, playing the
file ----....

\n<Minato>(...As I thought. It seems that the password
is inside this video.)

The video was about 15 minutes long, and it
would be a bit troublesome to watch it
all. However... I couldn't afford to
miss the password, so I stared at the
screen intently.

\n<Minato>(I hope it's found quickly... sigh... I
hope there aren't any puzzle elements or
anything...)

I couldn't help but let out a sigh... but
I quickly changed my mindset. And
then... as if resonating with me, the
screen switched to a simple black
background with only text displayed
----....
\n<Minato>...Huh...

My whole body froze at the unexpected
video... but it was only for a moment.
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]T-The one just now...

\F[\V[2]]...I instinctively closed the video file.
And then, I quickly looked around and
confirmed that I was alone in the room.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Are they telling me to watch that just
now... to show me such a video...)

\F[\V[2]]I'm angry at the trick that could be
interpreted as harassment. But... if I
were to confront Director Udo without
watching the video, I felt like I would
be made a fool of.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](It's annoying to be shaken up by something
like this and be seen as a child... And
if they say this is also part of the
lesson, if I were to play Reiko...)

I excitedly reach out my hand towards the
laptop. But... I couldn't help but be
curious about the entrance right behind
me, so I walk towards the door.

I feel relieved as I confirm the simple
key prepared on the door. And when I
close it... I turn my attention back to
the display once again ----...
